with version stable 20120901
with role    immune-system
with trait   solo stale
with info    last 20120901
with info    home http://sorcerer.silverice.org/
with info    cite "login assistance

When logging in a menu of window managers and shells is provided"

build(){
 mkdir  -pvm 755                        $DESTDIR/usr/sbin
 install -vm 644 $SCRIPT_DIR/help-login $DESTDIR/usr/sbin
}
